            </li>
        </xsl:if>
    </xsl:template>
        
    
    <!-- The third type of list is the glossary (gloss) list. It is essentially a list of pairs, consisting of
        a set of labels, each followed by an item. Unlike the ordered and bulleted lists, gloss is implemented
